.TH cdf-schema-discover 1  "cdf-schema-discover "
.SH NAME
cdf\-schema\-discover \- Discover the current physical source schema
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBcdf schema discover\fR [\fB\-q\fR|\fB\-\-quiet\fR] [\fB\-\-resource\fR] [\fB\-v\fR|\fB\-\-verbose\fR]... [\fB\-\-color\fR] [\fB\-\-no\-color\fR] [\fB\-\-progress\fR] [\fB\-\-unicode\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fIRESOURCE\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Discover the current physical source schema
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-q\fR, \fB\-\-quiet\fR
Suppress progress and non\-primary success narration
.TP
\fB\-\-resource\fR \fI<RESOURCE>\fR
Resource identifier (compatibility form)
.TP
\fB\-v\fR, \fB\-\-verbose\fR
Show evidence detail; repeat for diagnostics
.TP
\fB\-\-color\fR \fI<WHEN>\fR
Color policy: auto, always, or never
.br

.br
\fIPossible values:\fR
.RS 14
.IP \(bu 2
auto
.IP \(bu 2
always
.IP \(bu 2
never
.RE
.TP
\fB\-\-no\-color\fR
Compatibility alias for \-\-color never
.TP
\fB\-\-progress\fR \fI<WHEN>\fR
Progress policy: auto, always, or never
.br

.br
\fIPossible values:\fR
.RS 14
.IP \(bu 2
auto
.IP \(bu 2
always
.IP \(bu 2
never
.RE
.TP
\fB\-\-unicode\fR \fI<WHEN>\fR
Unicode policy: auto, always, or never
.br

.br
\fIPossible values:\fR
.RS 14
.IP \(bu 2
auto
.IP \(bu 2
always
.IP \(bu 2
never
.RE
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
[\fIRESOURCE\fR]
Resource identifier
